
<span class='GTTabs_titles'><b>Translation</b></span><br />
&#8220;Aja-ja-ja&#8230;&#8221; complained the Song thrush:<br />
&#8220;The Song thrush&#8217;s feet are freezing&#8221;</p>
<p>Here and then the ice would break from the Song thrush&#8217;s feet<br />
And waters would slowly flow</p>
<p>Oh, come up, early morning sun<br />
And let the Song thrush&#8217;s feet thaw<br />
&#8220;Aja-ja-ja-ja&#8221;</p>
<p>&#8220;Aja-ja-ja-ja&#8221;, complained the Song thrush:<br />
&#8220;The Song thrush&#8217;s feet are freezing&#8221;<br />
